{"tid":925783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"豪宅趙苑男子 以筆插喉尋死","createTime":"2018-12-03T03:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T07:24:37.000Z","uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f15a3723ca984e3f6619be8617500f9030a313d1","tid":925783,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:45:12.000Z","msg":"西區薄扶林域多利道趙苑，今早9時半許，一名男子被發現用筆插喉嚨尋死，救護員接報到場將他送院搶救，警方正展開調查。現場消息指，事主為一名年青男子，在屋苑一個辦公室內自殘，其同事發現報警處理，送院時喉嚨仍然插住筆。<br />\n趙苑共分3期，1期於1977年落成，共有11座洋房，其中10座於2005年初全數拆售，之後興建第2期及第3期，而卓能集團主席趙世曾曾自住於第1期。<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=T4XM9PkblQOSe8zhi732TZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=10228511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181203/58985756\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181203%2F58985756&d=T4XM9PkblQOSe8zhi732TZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=63dc4880\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181203%2F58985756&h=8bb282cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181203/58985756</a>"},{"pid":"b59d0d58115c9ab4c0aa25a60069377b681bf571","tid":925783,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:40:10.000Z","msg":"有錢都咁唔開心"},{"pid":"53341ebda66ba22ba617443b86c24ee68dd5a2fd","tid":925783,"uid":58852,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b59d0d58115c9ab4c0aa25a60069377b681bf571","tid":925783,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:40:10.00